<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="the-case">the case</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>事实；实情：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There is no simple answer, as is often the case in science.
没有简单的答案，这是科学中常有的事。</p><footer>2013 山东</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There is a misbelief that popcorn is calorie-free, but that is not the case.
有一种误解是爆米花不含热量，然而事实并非如此。</p><footer>2012 上海</footer></div></div>